{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852573181,"sessionID":"ses_286f06e2effeuBN2BJBTPCWHyH","part":{"id":"prt_d790fcddd001SyLOSoGFj20f5g","messageID":"msg_d790fc37c001NTSsJp91Of7joY","sessionID":"ses_286f06e2effeuBN2BJBTPCWHyH","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_dc1fb19405cf45f391b5905f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-015/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-015/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-015 ŌĆö PicoD ÕæĮõ╗żµē¦ĶĪī API\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the PicoD command execution API in `pkg/picod`.\n6: \n7: ## Base Specifications\n8: \n9: - **AR**: AR-015\n10: - **Module**: `pkg/picod`\n11: - **Language**: Go\n12: - **Size**: M\n13: - **Base Specs**: \n14:   - TBD\n15: \n16: ---\n17: \n18: ## Background\n19: \n20: TBD\n21: \n22: ---\n23: \n24: ## Requirements\n25: \n26: (To be defined)\n27: \n28: ---\n29: \n30: ## Acceptance Criteria\n31: \n32: (To be defined)\n\n(End of file - total 32 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-015 ŌĆö PicoD ÕæĮõ╗żµē¦ĶĪī API\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the PicoD command execution API in `pkg/picod`.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-015\n- **Module**: `pkg/picod`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n- **Base Specs**: \n  - TBD\n\n---\n\n## Background\n\nTBD","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-015/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775852573163,"end":1775852573178}}}}
